properties.title: Sprung
properties.description: Jon Matthies posted a photo: Springtime in Flagstaff brings flowers... and wind. I was wandering around the north end of NAU's campus this morning; with no hope of getting a sharp shot, I went the other way and used a .4 second exposure handheld to capture this image. Happy May Day! Or Beltane, depending on which part of the world your in. :)
